In [20]:
tdsvis.initialize_notebook(1200)

bus_real = df_real.copy()
bus_real = bus_real.unstack().reset_index().rename(columns={'level_0': 'name', 0: 'value'})
bus_im = df_imag.copy()
bus_im = bus_im.unstack().reset_index().rename(columns={'level_0': 'name', 0: 'value'})
start_date = df_real.index[0]
select = tdsvis.select()
initial_state = tdsvis.graphs.InitialState(current_time = str(start_date), color="#FF0000")
play = tdsvis.graphs.Play()

network = tdsvis.graphs.Network(g, pos, scale=1, height=400, width=340,size={'gen': 5, 'bus': 0.2}, legend=False)
network.subscribe = [ 'bus', 'bus_size']

busobj_real = tdsvis.graphs.Line(bus_real, x='timestamp', y='name', values='value', margin_left=75, xlab="Contingency", ylab="Real Voltage", scale=1, height=440, width=340) 
busobj_real.emit_color = tdsvis.color.ContinuousColor('bus', 0.1, 1, tdsvis.color.continuous.interpolateBlues)
busobj_real.emit_size = tdsvis.size.SizeRange('bus_size', 2, 5)
busobj_real.subscribe = ['bus']

busobj_im = tdsvis.graphs.Line(bus_im, x='timestamp', y='name', values='value', margin_left=75, xlab="Contingency", ylab="Imaginary Voltage", scale=1, height=440, width=340) 
busobj_im.subscribe = ['bus']

tdsvis.graphs.render([select, initial_state, play, network, busobj_real, busobj_im], standalone=False)
